59
00:03:45,830 --> 00:03:49,523
Space Station Remote Manipulator System,

60
00:03:49,523 --> 00:03:51,693
operated from inside the Station,

61
00:03:51,693 --> 00:03:55,198
and the assembly
of these new elements was done

62
00:03:55,198 --> 00:03:58,785
mainly with robotics, the robotic system.

63
00:03:59,488 --> 00:04:02,376
First of all, sometimes
the robotic system of the Shuttle

64
