the composition of cosmic rays,

123
00:07:31,850 --> 00:07:35,811
and try to detect antiparticles also,

124
00:07:35,811 --> 00:07:39,351
and try to resolve 
some of the questions that we have

125
00:07:39,351 --> 00:07:42,208
about the presence
of dark matter in the universe.

